<div class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-inset px-3 py-2.5">
  <% if mint %>
    <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted">Escrow mint: <span class="font-mono text-ink-secondary"><%= host %></span></p>
  <% end %>
  <p class="<%= "mt-1 " if mint %>text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
    A Cashu mint custodies the backing sats while they're locked. The lock is yours, but if the mint goes
    offline or fails, those funds can be lost, and the timelock refund needs the mint back online to pay out.
    Pick a mint you trust, and keep amounts modest while the platform is young.
  </p>
</div>
